@node IML-5 " MSG-5  Subject: How do I make a wood shingle roof"

Subject: How do I make a wood shingle roof
Date: Sun, 3 Jul 1994 14:05:00 -0400
From: david.wyand@canrem.com (David Wyand)

Hi Steve!

>Hi, what's a good way of making a shingle roof?

The best way to make a shingled roof is to use Essence volume II.  It
has a texture named Shingles which allows you to set colouring, size,
and shape parameters to your liking.  If you don't have Essence, get it.
 Or are you using a PC?

                                        -Dave
                                         david.wyand@canrem.com


