From: William Eric Donoho <donoho@iglou.com>

On Fri, 15 Jul 1994, Edwin Phillips wrote:

> 
> 	Hi,
> 
> 	I just bought the book "3D Modelling Lab" from the Waite Group 
> (can't remember the author's name offhand), which come with Imagine v2.0 
> for the PC and and image processing program for windows called 'PicMan'.  
> The book is good, and is devoted mostly to a tutorial on Imagine along 
