> 'reference' material for Imagine.  As a matter of fact, the book does not 
> even give any example of how to do animation! :(  The book does not cover 
> the Cycle Editor at all, either.
>   Are there in docs online that cover the features thouroughly?
>   Are there any hints/tips file on doing things with Imagine? 
>   Do PC Imagine users frequent this list?
>   Are there separate archives for PC users (Do the Amiga files work with 
> PC Imagine)?
