As regards 040 optimization...  RCS - maker of the fusion forty.. reports
that the 060 chip uses methods more closely aligned with the 030 than the
040.  That their 060 card makes Imagine run 3 to 7 times faster, yet yields
no significant speed increase for the 040 optimized Lightwave.  His reasoning
is that Imagine was never 040 optimized and is therefore optimized properly
for the 060.
