> 
> 
> 

  What is the data supposed to represent about the droplet?  If it 
represents the surface of the droplet, you may be able to convert the raw 
data into triagles, then DXF or POV input.  Is there a possibility that 
the surface will become disjoint?  This may make it more difficult to 
make a triagulated surface.  Another thing you might try is making a 
small sphere for each point (easy to do for POV) and see what it looks like.

  Ed

