Did you set your Numbers of Cycles to Perform, in the Action Editor for 
the object, I believe this works for brushwraps as well, just set it to 
how many times you want the animated brushwrap to loop. and it will tween 
it to fit.. Though it will work better if you calculate it so it will 
match up with your animation length.

=RRW=





