From: "" <williamp@triode.apana.org.au>

>  I know their are quite a few bugs on current version of Imagine. Seems
> to be one on lens flare's options. I alwais get this message: "can't
find > camera". > > I'd like to know for shure, is it a bug? ... > ...Or
do i just dont know how to use that option? > > > -- >

You just have the wrong texture installed.On the earlier upgrade discs 
the installer added faulty textures.The correct textures are on the main 
directory of the 1st disk in the 3.0 upgrade.Just copy them over to your 
textures/globals directory and everything will work.


