@node IML-318 " MSG-318  Subject: Re: Essence, Forge output on Imagine PC ?"

Subject: Re: Essence, Forge output on Imagine PC ?
Date: Wed, 27 Jul 94 13:51:59 PDT
From: "Charles Congdon" <CCONGDON@us.oracle.com>

> And most importantly are the generated textures portable to 
> Imagine PC (V2.0) ? 
 
Forge output is in IFF, TIFF, or JPEG format.  If any one of these formats are 
supported by Imagine PC (or any other renderer of interest), then you can 
generate your texture bitmaps on a FPU-equipped Amiga and send them over to 
the PC. 
	Cheers, 
	Charles 




